ggplot_missing <- function(data){
  df2 <- data %>% is.na %>% melt 

  ggplot(df2, aes(Var2, Var1, fill=value)) + 
    geom_raster() + 
    scale_fill_grey(name="", labels=c("Present", "Missing")) +
    theme_minimal() + 
    theme(axis.text.x  = element_text(angle=45, vjust=0.5)) + 
    labs(x = "Variables in Dataset",
         y = "Rows / observations")
}

### function for converting diagnosis codes
GcnvDiag <- function(df)
{
 colnames(df) <- c("diag")

for ( i in 1:nrow(df)) 
{
 dx<-as.character(df$diag[i])
 ln<-nchar(dx)

 pos <- regexpr("E", dx)
 if (pos[1]==1)
    {df$diag[i]<-"Other"}

 pos <- regexpr("V", dx)
 if (pos[1]==1)
    {df$diag[i]<-"Other"}

 
 if (ln >= 3)
   {
    keep <- substr(dx, 1, 3)
    flag<-0

    if (keep=="250")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Diabetes"
       flag<-1}

    if ((keep>="390"&keep<="459")|(keep=="785"))
      {df$diag[i]<-"Circulatory"
       flag<-1}

    if ((keep>="460"&keep<="519")|(keep=="786"))
      {df$diag[i]<-"Respiratory"
       flag<-1}

    if ((keep>="520"&keep<="579")|(keep=="787"))
      {df$diag[i]<-"Digestive"
       flag<-1}

    if ((keep>="580"&keep<="629")|(keep=="788"))
      {df$diag[i]<-"Genitourinary"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="800"&keep<="999")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Injury"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="710"&keep<="739")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Musculoskeletal"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="140"&keep<="239")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Neoplasms"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep=="780"|keep=="781"|keep=="782"|keep=="784")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Neoplasms"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="790"&keep<="799")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Neoplasms"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="240"&keep<="249")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Neoplasms"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="251"&keep<="279")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Neoplasms"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="680"&keep<="709")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Neoplasms"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="001"&keep<="139")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Neoplasms"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="290"&keep<="319")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Other"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="280"&keep<="289")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Other"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="320"&keep<="359")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Other"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="630"&keep<="679")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Other"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="360"&keep<="389")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Other"
       flag<-1}

    if (keep>="740"&keep<="759")
      {df$diag[i]<-"Other"
       flag<-1}

    if (flag==0)
      {df$diag[i]<-"Other"
       flag<-1}


   }
  else
   {
    df$diag[i]<-"Other"
   } 

}

 df
}

### function for handling new feature HbA1c
GnewDiag <- function(df)
{
 colnames(df) <- c("d1","d2","d3","dn")

for ( i in 1:nrow(df)) 
{
 dg1<-as.character(df$d1[i])
 dg2<-as.character(df$d2[i])
 dg3<-as.character(df$d3[i])

 if ((dg1=="Diabetes")|(dg2=="Diabetes")|(dg3=="Diabetes"))
    {df$dn[i]<-"Diabetes"}
 else
    {df$dn[i]<-df$d1[i]}

}

 df
}

### function for handling race
GcnvRace <- function(df)
{
 colnames(df) <- c("race")

for ( i in 1:nrow(df)) 
{
 ds<-as.character(df$race[i])

 if (ds=="Hispanic")
    {df$race[i]<-"Other"}

 if (ds=="Asian")
    {df$race[i]<-"Other"}

}

 df
}

### function for handling age
GcnvAge <- function(df)
{
 colnames(df) <- c("age")

for ( i in 1:nrow(df)) 
{
 ds<-as.character(df$age[i])

 if ((ds=="[0-10)") | (ds=="[10-20)") | (ds=="[20-30)"))
    {df$age[i]<-"<30"}
 else
    {
     if ((ds=="[30-40)") | (ds=="[40-50)") | (ds=="[50-60)"))
       {df$age[i]<-"30 to 60"}
     else
       {df$age[i]<-"60 to 100"}
    }

}

 df
}

### function for handling medical speciality
GcnvMspec <- function(df)
{
 colnames(df) <- c("msp")

for ( i in 1:nrow(df)) 
{
 ds<-as.character(df$msp[i])

 if ((ds=="?") | (ds=="Missing"))
    {df$msp[i]<-"Missing"}
 else
    {
     if ((ds=="Cardiology") | (ds=="Cardiology-Pediatric"))
       {df$msp[i]<-"Cardiology"}
     else
       {
        if (ds=="Family/GeneralPractice")
         {df$msp[i]<-"General practice"}
        else
         {
          if (ds=="InternalMedicine")
            {df$msp[i]<-"Internal medicine"}
          else
           {
              if ((ds=="Surgery-Cardiovascular") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Cardiovascular/Thoracic") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Colon&Rectal") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-General") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Maxillofacial") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Neuro") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Pediatric") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Plastic") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-PlasticwithinHeadandNeck") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Thoracic") 
                 |(ds=="Surgery-Vascular") 
                 |(ds=="SurgicalSpecialty")) 
               {df$msp[i]<-"Surgery"}
              else
               {df$msp[i]<-"Other"} 
           }
         }
       }
    }

}

 df
}

### function for handling new feature HbA1c
GcnvHbA1c <- function(df)
{
 colnames(df) <- c("res","chg","a1c")

for ( i in 1:nrow(df)) 
{
 rs<-as.character(df$res[i])
 ch<-as.character(df$chg[i])

 if (rs=="None")
    {df$a1c[i]<-"Not measured"}
 else
    {
     if (rs=="Norm")
       {df$a1c[i]<-"Normal"}
     else
       {
        if (((rs==">8")|(rs==">7"))&(ch=="No"))
         {df$a1c[i]<-"High and not changed"}
        else
         {
          if (((rs==">8")|(rs==">7"))&(ch=="Ch"))
            {df$a1c[i]<-"High and changed"}
          else
            {df$a1c[i]<-"WhatToDo"} 
         }
       }
    }

}

 df
}

### function for handling readmitted
GcnvRdm <- function(df)
{
 colnames(df) <- c("rdm")

for ( i in 1:nrow(df)) 
{
 ds<-as.character(df$rdm[i])

 if (ds=="NO")
       {df$rdm[i]<-"NoReadmission"}
 else
       {df$rdm[i]<-"Readmission"}
}

 df
}

### Function to draw confusion matrix
draw_confusion_matrix <- function(cm) {

  layout(matrix(c(1,1,2)))
  par(mar=c(2,2,2,2))
  plot(c(100, 345), c(300, 450), type = "n", xlab="", ylab="", xaxt='n', yaxt='n')
  title(girTITLE, cex.main=2)

  # create the matrix 
  rect(150, 430, 240, 370, col='#3F97D0')
  text(195, 435, 'NoReadmission', cex=1.2)
  rect(250, 430, 340, 370, col='#F7AD50')
  text(295, 435, 'Readmission', cex=1.2)
  text(125, 370, 'Predicted', cex=1.3, srt=90, font=2)
  text(245, 450, 'Actual', cex=1.3, font=2)
  rect(150, 305, 240, 365, col='#F7AD50')
  rect(250, 305, 340, 365, col='#3F97D0')
  text(140, 400, 'NoReadmission', cex=1.2, srt=90)
  text(140, 335, 'Readmission', cex=1.2, srt=90)

  # add in the cm results 
  res <- as.numeric(cm$table)
  text(195, 400, res[1], cex=1.6, font=2, col='white')
  text(195, 335, res[2], cex=1.6, font=2, col='white')
  text(295, 400, res[3], cex=1.6, font=2, col='white')
  text(295, 335, res[4], cex=1.6, font=2, col='white')

  # add in the specifics 
  plot(c(100, 0), c(100, 0), type = "n", xlab="", ylab="", main = "DETAILS", xaxt='n', yaxt='n')
  text(10, 85, names(cm$byClass[1]), cex=1.2, font=2)
  text(10, 70, round(as.numeric(cm$byClass[1]), 3), cex=1.2)
  text(30, 85, names(cm$byClass[2]), cex=1.2, font=2)
  text(30, 70, round(as.numeric(cm$byClass[2]), 3), cex=1.2)
  text(50, 85, names(cm$byClass[5]), cex=1.2, font=2)
  text(50, 70, round(as.numeric(cm$byClass[5]), 3), cex=1.2)
  text(70, 85, names(cm$byClass[6]), cex=1.2, font=2)
  text(70, 70, round(as.numeric(cm$byClass[6]), 3), cex=1.2)
  text(90, 85, names(cm$byClass[7]), cex=1.2, font=2)
  text(90, 70, round(as.numeric(cm$byClass[7]), 3), cex=1.2)

  # add in the accuracy information 
  text(30, 35, names(cm$overall[1]), cex=1.5, font=2)
  text(30, 20, round(as.numeric(cm$overall[1]), 3), cex=1.4)
  text(70, 35, names(cm$overall[2]), cex=1.5, font=2)
  text(70, 20, round(as.numeric(cm$overall[2]), 3), cex=1.4)
}

library(rpart.plot)
model<-rpart(readmitted ~ ., data=train)
predicted_class<- predict(model, test,type="class") 
table(predicted_class, test$readmitted)

## predicted_class NoReadmission Readmission
##   NoReadmission          2575         204
##   Readmission             177         419
misClasificError <- mean(as.character(predicted_class) != as.character(test$readmitted))
print(paste('Accuracy',1-misClasificError))
## [1] "Accuracy 0.887111111111111"
confusionMatrix(predicted_class, test$readmitted)

library(microbenchmark)
mbm<-microbenchmark(
m1<-rpart(readmitted ~ ., data=train),
m2<-predict(model, test,type="class"),
times=2)

mbm<-aggregate(x=mbm$time,by=list(Model=mbm$expr),FUN=mean)
mbm$x<-sum(mbm$x)
mm[8,]<-rbind("classification and Regression Trees","CART",mbm$x[1])

###Results and comparison
library(dplyr)
models<-length(cm)
results<-sapply (1:models, function(i) {c(cm[[i]][[1]],cm[[i]][[2]],cm[[i]]$overall[1:6])})
row.names(results)<-c("Description","Model",names(cm[[1]]$overall[1:6]))
results<-as.data.frame(t(results))
results[,3:8]<-sapply(3:8,function(i){results[,i]<-as.numeric(levels(results[,i])[results[,i]])})
results<-results[,-(4:8)]
results<-arrange(results,desc(Accuracy))

library(ggplot2)
library(gridExtra)
library(RColorBrewer)
res<-data.frame(Model=results$Model,Accuracy=results$Accuracy)
myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(12, "Set3")))
sc <- scale_colour_gradientn(colours = myPalette(256), limits=c(0.8, 1))
g<-ggplot(res,aes(x=reorder(Model,-Accuracy),y=Accuracy,fill=Model))+
        geom_bar(stat="identity")+
        coord_polar(theta="x",direction=1)+
        labs(x="Machine Learning Model",y="Prediction Accuracy")+
        theme(legend.position="bottom",legend.box="horizontal")+
        ggtitle('Diabetes Dataset Accuracy Performance')
g

mm1<-mm
mm1$Speed<-as.numeric(mm1$Speed)
mm1$Speed<-1 - (mm1$Speed/sum(mm1$Speed))
mm1<-arrange(mm1,desc(Speed))
myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(12, "Set3")))

        coord_polar(theta="x",direction=1)+
